there was not enough proof of state 
incapacity or inertia in the investigation. In 
S&#227;o Paulo, the Sapopemba Human Rights 
Centre has used the threat of seeking an 
Appeal Court authorization to unblock a 
torture case subjected to unnecessary 
delays in the respective state Supreme 
Court. 
