<p>The existing Danish control regimes are 
adequate to ensure that the relevant 
authorities have the necessary possibilities 
to intervene should the authorities receive 
concrete knowledge of an extraordinary 
rendition heading towards or being in 
Danish, Greenlandic or Faroese airspace.7 
