<p>(t) Due to extremely harsh prison 
conditions and routine practice of 
torture, the Al-Jafr Correction and 
Rehabilitation Centre be closed without 
delay 
</p>
<p>Detainees are routinely beaten and 
subjected to corporal punishment 
amounting to torture. The isolation and 
harshness of the desert environment 
compounds the already severe 
conditions of the prisoners.  
</p>
<p>The Government closed Al-Jafr 
Prison in December 2006.  
</p>
