prosecution of 31 members of the 
Nepalese Army, Nepal Police and 
Armed Police Force, largely in 
connection with killings which had 
occurred in the context of the 
protests, but no action has been 
taken to initiate prosecutions by the 
authorities. No one has been 
prosecuted for the many cases of 
serious beatings which occurred in 
the context of the protests.  
</i></p>
<p><i>There have been no independent 
