<p><b><i>Non-governmental sources:</i></b><i> Severe problems in securing funding to 
assist with the rehabilitation of torture victims exist. 
</i></p>
<p><b>Government</b>: There was no increase in funding for the rehabilitation 
of victims of torture since 2008. Humanitarian aid was provided in the 
framework of projects for rehabilitation of victims of torture. 
</p>
