<p>Article 3 of Supreme Court resolution &#8220;On the 
Application of Some of the Norms of the 
Criminal Procedure Legislation on Admission of 
Proof&#8221; of 24 September 2004 prohibits the use 
of evidence obtained by any illegal means of 
investigation; 
</p>
<p>Between 2004 and 2007 about 50 criminal cases 
were returned for additional investigation 
because the evidence was excluded as having 
